summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3463, for the improvement of the alley between blocks 7 and 8 and 17 and 18, Euclid Addition, being the alley between 50th Avenue Southwest and 51st Avenue Southwest, from Genesee Street to West Alaska Street, all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 42884 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
